txt.en: This bundle is clearly part of a supply delivery. Amid the claw and bite marks the worm inflicted upon it, you see the trace of the Elven name, 'Gwingris.'\n\nGwingris lies to the west. You should look for someone there who might know something about the satchel.

'What do you bring to me?

'It is as I feared. Our latest delivery from Rivendell fell prey to the worms of Pend Eregion. We have long known of the worms; but until now they proved little more than a hinderance.

'Increased aggression from the worms spells grave news for our way-post.'
You have found what appears to be part of a supply delivery to the Elf-camp at Gwingris.
Gwingris lies to the west of the ruined supply delivery.\n\nYou should take the satchel you found to the Elf-camp at Gwingris.
